json.name: Slums of Kerning (a Hut)
json.description:
The hut leans to one side, its walls patched with scrap wood and cloth.
Its roof is made of bent tin sheets, held down with stones and rope.
The doorway hangs open, creaking in the wind like it might fall any minute.
